{"tid":1538261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（緊記）林鄭讓步唔係放鬆手腳既一刻呀！","createTime":"2019-09-04T06:45:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T11:54:23.000Z","uid":124045,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"593b78a2fedc944cb77bda5b1f5792d12b315d28","tid":1538261,"uid":124045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:45:08.000Z","msg":"「敵進我退，敵駐我擾，敵疲我打，敵退我追」<br />\n<br />\n記唔記得呢句名句呀<br />\n以子之矛 攻子之盾<br />\n<br />\n佢讓步唔係因為想釋出善意<br />\n而係佢輸到無棋可行啦！<br />\n證明我地行岩棋 佢地係驚美國復會 驚十一國慶呀<br />\n係佢地心急啦！<br />\n<br />\n以家我地要既唔係同佢和談<br />\n而係要追擊佢逼迫佢！<br />\n最後既目標係咩野呀？<br />\n大家想要既係咩野呀？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五！大！訴！求！ <br />\n缺！一！不！可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當初我地all in 左<br />\n以家要贏就要贏到盡！<br />\n政府豪賭係要付出代價嫁！"},{"pid":"cffd3265913a237a564a3ca4da15ffab68e1db38","tid":1538261,"uid":124045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:45:25.000Z","msg":"大家幫手推上去！"},{"pid":"efe9a33c6d2cdcd3d0e645cf0999aa98537c6dd3","tid":1538261,"uid":124045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:45:42.000Z","msg":"追擊佢"},{"pid":"00a67a8bdd51ec98ba7d4d45e9bfd945bdd840e2","tid":1538261,"uid":124045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:45:52.000Z","msg":"唔好放過佢"},{"pid":"5db67df7ebd9cfbe7b6801a6389bdb26c4ec75f4","tid":1538261,"uid":124045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:46:10.000Z","msg":"你地係咪忘記左七位義士"},{"pid":"983480ded8772630d9ad936fd535e737738ade23","tid":1538261,"uid":124045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:46:22.000Z","msg":"幾位手足既眼"},{"pid":"b110356a61fa3154d69ad73194746028be337130","tid":1538261,"uid":124045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:46:37.000Z","msg":"手足既手腳"},{"pid":"72dc75e5ffda4c5c82e4e3d69e598c0ae31ff924","tid":1538261,"uid":124045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0